Agiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa unug ku jira dusha sare ee unugyada (dusha sare ee unugyada) ee unugyada, xididdada, wadnaha, kelyaha, iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay xakameysaa waxqabadka angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa heerarka angiotensin-II iyadoo kor u qaadaya Ang ((1-7) si ay u noqoto daawo laga yaabo in lagu daweeyo cudurrada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa sidii horudhac u ah ka hortagga cudurada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Dadka waxaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Qalabka loo yaqaan 'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2' wuxuu ka kooban yahay zinc oo ah metalloenzyme oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada dhiigga iyo unugyada kale.
borotiinka ACE2 wuxuu ka kooban yahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waxay mar mar dhex martaa maqaarka hareeraha jirka, iyadoo qaybaha ugu muhiimsan ay ka muuqdaan dusha sare ee unugyada iyo muruqyada kale.
Meelaha ka baxsan ACE2 waxaa laga soo saaraa maqaarka oo waxaa u wareejiyaa kiimiko kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase, taas oo ka dibna borotiinka soo saaray loo wareejiyo dhiigga oo ugu dambeyntii loo beddelo dheecaan.
ACE2 waxaa lagu ogaadaa inta badan xubnaha jirka: ACE2 waxay ku xidhan tahay unugyada maqaarka gaar ahaan unugyada xayawaanka nooca II ee derbiyada sanbabada, unugyada xayawaanka yaryar, unugyada xididdada iyo unugyada xididdada dhiigga, iyo unugyada muruqyada ee unugyada jirka ee inta badan xubnaha jirka.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa sidoo kale lagu helaa maqaarka maskaxda, lafdhabarta, hypothalamus, iyo maskaxda.
Waxqabadka ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa hagaajinta ACE
ACE waxay ku xidhan tahay hormoonka angiotensin I ee angiotensin II ee xannibaadda dhiigga.
ACE2 waxay ku xirantahay carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine oo ka soo jeeda angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) waxayna u kala baxdaa angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale ku xirnaan kartaa xidhiidhada kala duwan ee xidhiidhka, oo ay ku jiraan [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa wareegga maqaarka ee loo yaqaan 'neutral amino acid receptor SLC6A19' oo loo maleynayo inay sabab u tahay cudurka Hartnup.
Sida borotiinka maqaarka lagu qaado, ACE2 waxay u shaqeysaa sidii albaabada ugu muhiimsan ee difaaca ee qaar ka mid ah fayrasyada corona, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus-ka SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus-ka COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, isku xirnaanta borotiinka S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee ACE2 ee dusha sare ee unugyada waxay keentaa in fayraska iyo unugyada ay ka soo baxaan goobtooda oo ay ku soo noqdaan unugyada.
Nidaamkan soo galootiga ah wuxuu sidoo kale u baahan yahay in la furo borotiinka S ee loo yaqaan 'serine protease TMPRSS2', oo la baaro si loo ogaado isticmaalka daaweynta. Tani waxay keentay in qaar ka mid ah fikradaha la yiraahdo in hoos u dhigista heerka ACE2 ee unugyada, ay ka caawin karto difaaca cudurka.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, hay'ado cilmi baaris iyo nidaamyo kala duwan ayaa taageeraya sii wadida ACE inhibitor oo loo yaqaan daaweynta ARB.
Daraasad la sameeyay oo si taxadar leh loo sameeyay oo laga soo xigtay daraasad cilmiyeed oo la daabacay July 11, 2012, ayaa lagu ogaaday in "isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ay 34% ka yar tahay khatarta sambabada marka loo eego daawooyinka kale ee la soo jeediyay
"Kale, khatarta sambabada ayaa hoos u dhacday bukaannada la daweeyay ACE inhibitors oo ay u badan tahay inay sambabada qabtaan, gaar ahaan kuwa qaba cudurka wadnaha
Isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ayaa sidoo kale la rumeysan yahay inay yareynayaan dhimashada sambabada, inkastoo saameyntu aysan ahayn mid aad u daran sida khatarta sambabada"
ACE2 bini'aadamka ee dib loo soo saaray (rhACE2) ayaa loo maleynayaa inay tahay daaweynta ugu horreysa ee cudurka neefta ee daran, waxaana la ogaaday inay hagaajinayso xakameynta dareenka iyo socodka neefta ee dhallinyarada qaba cudurka neefta ee lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Dhibaatada rhACE2 ee aadanaha waxay qaadataa 10 saacadood, shaqada waxay bilaabataa 30 daqiiqo marka la daro waqtiga shaqada (waqtiga la qiyaasay) ee 24 saacadood.
Natiijooyinka daraasado kala duwan ayaa muujinaya in rhACE2 ay noqon karto daaweyn rajo leh oo loogu talagalay kuwa aan u dulqaadan karin xakameynta nidaamka renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitors) ama cudurada ay ku kordhayso wareegga angiotensin II. RhACE2 lagu shubay ayaa lagu baaray tijaabooyin caafimaad oo lagu daaweynayo cudurada la xiriira cudurrada suuxdinta.
