Shiinaha, dowladda Shiinaha, oo kaashanaysa Alipau, ayaa soo saartay barnaamij u oggolaanaya muwaadiniintooda inay tijaabiyaan haddii ay xiriir la lahaayeen COVID-19.
Waxaa loo isticmaalaa in ka badan 200 magaalo oo Shiinaha ah, Singapore waxaa loo isticmaalaa barnaamijka loo yaqaan 'TraceTogether'.
