Ilaa 14 Abriil 2020, barnaamijka ayaa weli la xaqiijinayaa dukaamada Google Play iyo Apple App Store.
12-kii Abriil, dowladdu waxay shaacisay in barnaamijka la socoshada xiriirka uu ku jiro marxaladda ugu dambeysa ee horumarinta, waxaana la filayaa inuu bilaabo toddobaadyo gudahood. Barnaamij la mid ah ayaa laga diyaarinayaa Ireland, iyo Faransiiska ("StopCovid").
Australia iyo New Zealand waxay tixgelinayaan barnaamijyada TraceTogether ee Singapore iyo borotokoolka BlueTrace. Ruushka ayaa qorsheynaya inuu bilaabo barnaamij geofencing ah oo loogu talagalay bukaannada COVID-19 ee ku nool Moscow, oo loogu talagalay inay ka hortagaan inay ka baxaan guryahooda.
Ross Anderson, oo ah borofisar ku takhasusay injineernimada amniga ee Jaamacadda Cambridge, ayaa tilmaamay dhibaatooyinka ka dhalan kara barnaamijyada ku saleysan, oo ay ku jiraan in ay u muuqdaan kuwo wax ku ool ah iyo kuwa aan wax ku ool ahayn marka barnaamijka la isticmaalo dadka.
Si loo xaliyo dhibaatooyinka barnaamijyada cudurka 'coronavirus' ee khatarta ah ama khatarta ah, Apple waxay xaddiday shirkadaha ay ku dari karaan barnaamijyada la xiriira cudurka 'coronavirus' App Store, iyadoo kaliya ay oggolaaneyso shirkadaha ama shirkadaha la aqoonsan yahay.
Google iyo Amazon ayaa sidoo kale sameeyay xaddidaad la mid ah.
