Waxay ku saleysan tahay cilmi baaris laga sameeyay warbixinta "Apps Gone Rogue: Ilaalinta Asturnaantaada ee Cudur-galka" (Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic) oo la daabacay bishii Maarso 2020. Nidaam kale oo la mid ah ayaa ah barnaamijka SafeTrace ee Enigma MPC, oo ah shirkad horumarineed oo ah tikniyoolajiyad qarsoodi ah oo horey ugu sugnaa MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace waxay abuurtaa tiknoolajiyad aan khatar lahayn oo u oggolaanaysa dadka isticmaala inay la wadaagaan macluumaadka sirta ah ee goobta iyo caafimaadka dadka kale iyo maamulayaasha, iyada oo aan wax khatar ah lagu gelin asturnaanta.
